abstract: Governments reports will include third-quarter gross domestic product and new home sales for September, and companies reporting earnings will include Caterpillar, Facebook, 3M, AT&T and Apple.
snippet: Governments reports will include third-quarter gross domestic product and new home sales for September, and companies reporting earnings will include Caterpillar, Facebook, 3M, AT&T and Apple.
lead_paragraph: ECONOMIC REPORTS Data to be released will include new home sales for September (Wednesday); weekly jobless claims, durable goods for September and pending home sales for September (Thursday); and third-quarter gross domestic product and the Thomson Reuters/University of Michigan consumer sentiment index for October (Friday).
